    "Their independence, IAM agents are key in handling issues and maintaining consistency and compliance in access control.",
    "Their taxonomy shows that they all perform certain functions, but at the same time highlights the fact that their branding, permissions and cost arrangements vary.",
    "When this is the case, autonomous security agents should be able to recognize contexts and enforce IAM policies properly on each platform they protect.",
    "2018) studies obstacles and challenges in the use of IAM for cloud computing, paying special attention to situations involving many users and services handled by third parties.",
